Regulation (EEC) No 3785/85 is hereby amended as follows:
(a) the following countries shall be added to Annex I: Brazil, Mexico, Pakistan;
(b) the Annex to this Regulation shall be inserted in Annex II.

Regulation (EEC) No 182/86 is hereby amended as follows:
(a) the following countries shall be deleted from Annex II: Brazil, Mexico, Pakistan;
(b) the quantitative limits for Brazil, Mexico and Pakistan shall be deleted from Annex III.
